{"id": "fe37qd", "title": "Random Chance Betting", "selftext": "I want to see if I actually perform better than random chance, so I'm starting with $1000 and doing this every Monday morning until I run out of money.\n\nCoin Toss, DIA or QQQ\n\n|Heads|DIA||\n|:-|:-|:-|\n|Tails|QQQ||\n\nDie Roll I, Call or Put:\n\n|Die Roll|Call or Put|Weeks Out|\n|:-|:-|:-|\n|1|Put|1|\n|2|Put|2|\n|3|Put|3|\n|4|Call|1|\n|5|Call|2|\n|6|Call|3|\n\nDie Roll II, Strike Price:\n\n|Die Roll|Stike (% above for call, below for put)||\n|:-|:-|:-|\n|1|5%||\n|2|10%||\n|3|15%||\n|4|20%||\n|5|25%||\n|6|30%||\n\nDie Roll III, Amount Bought\n\n|Die Roll|% of Available Cash in My Account||\n|:-|:-|:-|\n|1|10%||\n|2|20%||\n|3|30%||\n|4|40%||\n|5|50%||\n|6|60%||\n\nDie Roll IV, Limit Order (for closing sale)\n\n|Die Roll|Multiplier of Bought At|Gain|\n|:-|:-|:-|\n|1|1.5|50%|\n|2|2.0|100%|\n|3|2.5|150%|\n|4|3.0|200%|\n|5|3.5|250%|\n|6|4.0|300%|\n\nEdit; tl,dr;  \n\nDIA Call 27 Mar; Strike = round(MondayOpeningPrice \\*1.15);  NumberContracts = int(500/OptionPrice);  Strike = OptionPrice \\* 1.5;", "created_utc": 1583446677.0, "permalink": "/r/wallstreetbets/comments/fe37qd/random_chance_betting/", "is_self": true}